<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
<title>xml:space attribute of pre element</title>
<style type="text/css">
@namespace xml "http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace";
[xml|space="preserve"]
	{content:"PASS"}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<pre xml:space="preserve">FAIL</pre>
<p>You should see word pass above</p>
</body>
